### Guest - GET ALL
GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests
Accept: application/json

### Guest - GET BY ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests/1
Accept: application/json

### Guest - GET BY STATUS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/guests/status/ATTENDING
Accept: application/json

### Guest - POST
POST http://localhost:8080/api/guests
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "New Guest",
  "status": "NO_RESPONSE"
}

### Guest - PUT
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/guests/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Guest",
  "status": "ATTENDING"
}

### Guest - PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/guests/1
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "status": "NOT_ATTENDING"
}

### Guest - DELETE
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/guests/1
Accept: application/json

